                 href="http://mssa.altfindingaids.library.yale.edu/mssa.ms.0525/mssa_ms_0525_genealogical_charts.pdf"
                 linktitle="Genealogical Charts"
                 show="new">Genealogical Charts</ref>.</p>  
      </bioghist>
  
